# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok federal reserve chairman ben bernanke monday briefed president barack obama about the path ahead for the stricken us economy , the white house said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "White"
                  :op2 "House"))
      :ARG1 (b / brief-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Ben"
                        :op2 "Bernanke")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (r / reserve-01
                              :mod (f / federal))
                        :ARG2 (c / chairman)))
            :ARG1 (p2 / person
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Barack"
                        :op2 "Obama")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (p3 / president)))
            :ARG2 (p4 / path
                  :direction (a / ahead)
                  :beneficiary (e / economy
                        :poss (w / we)
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / strike-01)))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (m / monday))))

                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Newcastle"))))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (l / leave-out-03
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (s2 / squad
                        :poss (c / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Australia")))
                  :purpose (q / qualify-02
                        :ARG1 t

                              :mod (w2 / world))

                              :mod (n4 / next))))))

# ::alignments
(d / donate-01
      :ARG0 (a / authority
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Sudan")))
      :ARG1 (m / monetary-quantity
            :quant 1000000000
            :unit (d2 / dollar))
      :ARG2 (t / town
            :name n
            :op1 "Darfur")
      :ARG1-of (r / recapture-01
            :ARG0 (t2 / troop
                  :mod (g / government-organization
                        :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01)))
            :time (w / week
                  :mod (t3 / this))
            :time (a2 / after
                  :op1 (f / fight-01
                        :ARG0 t2
                        :ARG1 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (r2 / rebel-01))
                        :duration (t4 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 3
                              :unit (w2 / week))))))

# ::alignments
(r / rampage-01
      :ARG0 (e / elephant
            :ARG0-of (s / stray-01
                  :direction (o / out-of
                        :op1 (p / park
                              :mod (n / nation)))))
      :ARG1 (v / village
            :location (d / district
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Illustration")
                  :location (n3 / north
                        :part-of (c / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Uganda")))))
      :mod (a / again)
      :ARG0-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (k / kill-01
                        :ARG0elephant (p2 / person
                              :quant 2
                              :ARG0-of (f / farm-01)))
                  :op2 (ii / injure-01
                        :ARG0elephant (p3 / person
                              :mod (o2 / other)))
                  :time (c3 / come-03
                        :ARG1 (s2 / season
                              :mod (h / harvest-01))))))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Bombardier"
                  :op2 "Aerospace"))
      :ARG1 (s2 / sign-02
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (a / agree-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (c2 / credit
                              :mod (l / lease-01
                                    :ARG0 (c3 / company
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "Cdb")
                                          :ARG1-of (b / base-01
                                                :location (c4 / country
                                                      :name (n3 / name
                                                            :op1 "China"))))))
                        :op2 (c5 / credit
                              :mod (f / finance-01)))
                  :ARG2 (c6 / customer)
                  :quant (u / up-to
                        :op1 (m / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000000
                              :unit (d / dollar
                                    :mod c4
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "US"))))))
      :ARG2 c3
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::alignments
(r / record-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Malaysia"))
      :ARG1 (d / deficit
            :mod (t / trade-01)
            :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (l / low-04
                        :ARG1 d)
                  :ARG3 (m / more)
                  :ARG4 (p / period
                        :ARG1-of (c2 / correspond-02)
                        :part-of (y / year
                              :mod (l2 / last)))))
      :time (m2 / month
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :part-of (y2 / year
                  :mod (t2 / this))))

            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (g / guard-01
                        :ARG1 (b / border))
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "India")))
            :ARG1 (p2 / person
                  :quant 2
                  :mod (r / religious-group
                        :name n
                        :op1 "Muslim"))
            :ARG1-of (d / die-01))
      :location (h / here)
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (a2 / attack-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (p4 / police)
                              :ARG2 (o2 / officer)))
                  :instrument (g2 / grenade)
                  :ARG1-of (f / fail-01))))
